ed="T" n="0824c17"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0824c17"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000020295"><placeName>齊州</placeName><placeName>靈巖寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A012146">道鑒</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0824c18"/><persName key="A012146">釋道鑒</persName>，姓<name>馮</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0824sgsz14"/>人<anchor xml:id="end0824sgsz14"/>。未知從來，而居<placeName key="PL000000020295"><placeName>歷<lb
ed="T" n="0824c19"/>下</placeName><placeName>靈巖山寺</placeName></placeName>，蹤迹神異，不測僧也。<date notBefore-iso="+0806-01-29" key="j20154742020967" notAfter-iso="+0821-02-12"><name>元和</name>中</date>，有<lb
ed="T" n="0824c20"/><persName key="A012147">馮生</persName>者，亦<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也，以明經<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1579"/>調選未捷，因<lb
ed="T" n="0824c21"/>僑寄<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>。一日見老僧來詣<persName key="A012147">馮</persName>居，謂之曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0824c22"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A012147">汝</ref>，<ref type="person" target="#A012146">吾</ref>姓也。」因相與往還，僅于歲餘，遂注擬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1658"/><lb
ed="T" n="0824c23"/>作尉于東<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>。方務治裝，<persName key="A012146">鑒</persName>負錫來告去。<lb
ed="T" n="0824c24"/><persName key="A012147">馮</persName>問：「<ref type="person" target="#A012146">師</ref>去，安所詣乎？」<persName key="A012146">鑒</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012146">吾</ref>廬在<placeName key="PL000000020295"><placeName>齊州</placeName><placeName>靈巖<lb
ed="T" n="0824c25"/></placeName></placeName>之西廡下，薄遊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g674"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">神京</placeName><ptr target="#n2353"/>，至今正十年矣。幸得<lb
ed="T" n="0824c26"/>與<ref type="person" target="#A012147">子</ref>遊，今歸舊所，故來相別。然<ref type="person" target="#A012147">吾子</ref>尉于<lb
ed="T" n="0824c27"/><placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>鄉，道出<placeName key="PL000000020295">靈巖寺</placeName>下，當宜一訪<ref type="person" target="#A012146">我</ref>也。」<persName key="A012147">馮</persName>諾<lb
ed="T" n="0824c28"/>之曰：「謹受教矣。」數日<ptr target="#n529"/>，<persName key="A012147">馮</persName>出<placeName key="PL000000043334">關</placeName>，東之赴任，<lb
ed="T" n="0824c29"/>至<placeName key="PL000000020295">靈巖寺</placeName>門，立馬望曰：「豈非<persName key="A012146">鑒<roleName>師</roleName></persName>所居寺<pb ed="T" n="0825a" xml:id="T50.2061.0825a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825a01"/><anchor xml:id="beg0825001"/>乎<anchor xml:id="end0825001"/>？」即入訪之。時一僧在庭，<persName key="A012147">馮</persName>問：「<persName key="A012146">道鑒<roleName>上人</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0825a02"/>廬舍安在？」僧曰：「<ref type="place" target="#PL000000020295">此寺</ref>無<persName key="A012146">道鑒</persName>。」<persName key="A012147">馮</persName>疑異，默而計<lb
ed="T" n="0825a03"/>曰：「<persName key="A012146">鑒<roleName>公</roleName></persName>純直，豈欺<ref type="person" target="#A012147">我</ref>乎？」於是獨遊<ref type="place" target="#PL000000020295">寺</ref>中，行<lb
ed="T" n="0825a04"/>至西廡下，忽見壁畫一僧，與<persName key="A012146">鑒<roleName>師</roleName></persName>貌同<ptr target="#n530"/>。<persName key="A012147">馮</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0825a05"/>大驚嗟：「<persName key="A012146">鑒<roleName>師</roleName></persName>果異人歟？且能降神與<ref type="person" target="#A012147">我</ref>交。」久<lb
ed="T" n="0825a06"/>之，視其真相旁題云：「<name>馮</name>氏子，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也。年<lb
ed="T" n="0825a07"/>十歲學浮圖法，以道行有聞，卒年七十八。」<lb
ed="T" n="0825a08"/><persName key="A012147">馮</persName>閱其題，方悟云「<ref type="person" target="#A012147">汝</ref>，<ref type="person" target="#A012146">吾</ref>姓也」，言非謬矣。一<lb
ed="T" n="0825a09"/>說<placeName key="PL000000009928">蘇州</placeName>西去城二十許里，有<placeName key="PL000000010068">靈巖山寺</placeName>，西北<lb
ed="T" n="0825a10"/>廡下畫沙門形，云是<placeName key="PL000000000138">梁</placeName><date from-iso="+0516-02-20" key="j19095751909929" to-iso="+0517-02-08"><name>天監</name>十五年</date>作遊方<lb
ed="T" n="0825a11"/>居士狀，經過<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010068">山寺</ref>，寓過宵宿，而於僧厨借<lb
ed="T" n="0825a12"/>筆硯，僧眾皆不留意。詰旦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g408"/>，僧遍搜索而亡<lb
ed="T" n="0825a13"/>有客，見殿隅畫一<name>梵</name>僧，面骨權奇，膚色皴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1659"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825a14"/>黑，眉長<anchor xml:id="beg0825002"/>且<anchor xml:id="end0825002"/>垂，眸子電轉，眥間青白，昂鼻方<lb
ed="T" n="0825a15"/>口，張脣露齒，擎拳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1660"/>倚右肩之上，身屈可長一<lb
ed="T" n="0825a16"/>丈五寸，衣麁<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>衲</sic><corr>納</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz1"/>袈裟，臂擐大珠，徒跣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1661"/>。眾見<lb
ed="T" n="0825a17"/>驚懾，莫測其來。遠近咸格<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1662"/>，有焚香<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz2"/><anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz3"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz3"/>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0825a18"/>有請福<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz4"/>禳<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz4"/>災者。或於晴夜，殿中析窣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1663"/>，聞有<lb
ed="T" n="0825a19"/>行道之聲，由是鳥雀不敢污踐簷楹之間<lb
ed="T" n="0825a20"/>矣。然則鄉人謂之<persName key="A012156">靈巖和尚</persName>，或云<persName key="A012156">靈巖聖僧</persName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0825a21"/>甞見形謂一老姥曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012156">貧道</ref>好食茭粽<ptr target="#n2354"/>。」疑是<lb
ed="T" n="0825a22"/>聖者，翌日持<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>簟</sic><corr>簞</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz5"/>入殿供養，<anchor xml:id="beg0825003"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>乞</sic><corr>迄</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0825003"/>今年別<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1578"/>三月<lb
ed="T" n="0825a23"/>三日民競送之，以<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz6"/>菰<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz6"/>蔣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1664"/>葉角黍米𤅢<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1575"/>之，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0825a24"/>人謂之茭粽也。<placeName key="PL000000000106">唐</placeName><date from-iso="+0713-02-04" key="j19815121981836" to-iso="+0713-12-25"><name>先天</name>二年</date>，<persName key="A012149"><persName>陸</persName><persName>魯公</persName></persName>子疾，醫<lb
ed="T" n="0825a25"/>工未驗<ptr target="#n2356"/>，<persName key="A012149">公</persName>憂慮增劇。門遇一僧分衛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g602"/>，屈入，<lb
ed="T" n="0825a26"/>遂索水器含噀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1645"/>之，即時病間<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1588"/>。<persName key="A012149">魯公</persName>喜，贈物頗<lb
ed="T" n="0825a27"/>豐，了不迴視。遂問：「<ref type="person" target="#A012156">和尚</ref>居處何寺？」答曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012156">貧<lb
ed="T" n="0825a28"/>道</ref>住<placeName key="PL000000009996"><placeName>蘇州</placeName><placeName>吳縣</placeName></placeName>西<placeName key="PL000000010068">靈巖寺</placeName>。<ref type="person" target="#A012152">郎君</ref>為官<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>，望<lb
ed="T" n="0825a29"/>入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010068">寺</ref>相尋。」斯須已去。未久，調補尚書<anchor xml:id="beg0825004"/>刑<anchor xml:id="end0825004"/>部<pb ed="T" n="0825b" xml:id="T50.2061.0825b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825b01"/>郎，續遷<placeName key="PL000000032245">桂州</placeName>廉使。常念當年救病之僧，迂<lb
ed="T" n="0825b02"/>路<placeName key="PL000000009928">姑蘇</placeName>，入<placeName key="PL000000010068">靈巖寺</placeName>覓焉。乃說其形貌，合寺<lb
ed="T" n="0825b03"/>僧云：「非此所有。」<persName key="A012152">陸</persName>盡日徘徊不忍去，忽於<lb
ed="T" n="0825b04"/>殿中見聖者形，曰：「往年療某者，<ref type="person" target="#A012156">此僧</ref>也。」寺<lb
ed="T" n="0825b05"/>僧說其由致，通感難知。<persName key="A012152">陸</persName>捨錢數萬，備香<lb
ed="T" n="0825b06"/>火之資，却留旬日，供養方去。又<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010068">寺</ref>中淨人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g695"/>每<lb
ed="T" n="0825b07"/>於像前占燭燈，添油助燼，意盜油塗髮<lb
ed="T" n="0825b08"/>耳。居無何<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g493"/>，其髮焦卷而墮，傍人勸令<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz8"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz8"/>懺，<lb
ed="T" n="0825b09"/>別買麻膏增炷，平復如初。又<persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>將廢佛<lb
ed="T" n="0825b10"/>教也，近<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010068">寺</ref>有<persName key="A012153">陸宣</persName>者，夢聖者云：「受<ref type="person" target="#A012153">弟子</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0825b11"/>供施年深，今來相別，且歸西天去也。」<persName key="A012153">宣</persName>急<lb
ed="T" n="0825b12"/>命畫工圖寫真貌。至<date from-iso="+0845-02-15" key="j20297362030089" to-iso="+0846-02-03"><name>會昌</name>五年</date>，毀拆寺宇，<lb
ed="T" n="0825b13"/>方知告別之意焉。距<date from-iso="+0866-01-25" key="j20373852037768" to-iso="+0867-02-12"><name>咸通</name>七年</date>蝗災，爾時<lb
ed="T" n="0825b14"/>彌空亘野，食人苗稼，至于入人家食繒帛<lb
ed="T" n="0825b15"/>之物。百姓徬徨，莫能為計。時民人<persName key="A012154">吳延讓</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0825b16"/>等率耆艾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g874"/>數十百人詣像前焚香泣告，即<lb
ed="T" n="0825b17"/>日蟲飛越境焉。<date from-iso="+0878-02-10" key="j20417842042137" to-iso="+0879-01-29"><name>乾符</name>五年</date>，寺眾當詣闕乞<lb
ed="T" n="0825b18"/>鐘歸寺，差僧<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz9"/>選日<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz9"/>登途。聖者先入右神策<lb
ed="T" n="0825b19"/>軍本局，預陳囑託。及正請鐘僧到，見司吏，<lb
ed="T" n="0825b20"/>怪問：「數日前有僧來，云隷<placeName key="PL000000010068"><placeName>蘇州</placeName><placeName>靈巖山寺</placeName></placeName>。」<lb
ed="T" n="0825b21"/>其僧曰：「某行無伴侶。」後右軍胥因事遊<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0825b22"/>見壁畫云：「此是<date from-iso="+0878-08-07" key="j20419622041990" to-iso="+0878-09-04">七月</date>中曾來司內計會鐘<lb
ed="T" n="0825b23"/>僧也。」然<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>中極彰靈異，且不測厥由。曾有<lb
ed="T" n="0825b24"/><name>梵</name>僧來，<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz10"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz10"/>畫像云：「<persName key="A023508">智積菩薩</persName>何緣在此？」<anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz11"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz11"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825b25"/>嗟彌久，而自此號「<persName key="A012156">智積應身</persName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1665"/>」也。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0825b2601"><lb
ed="T" n="0825b26"/>系曰：同異之說，史氏多之，今詳寺曰<placeName key="PL000000010068">靈巖</placeName>，僧<lb
ed="T" n="0825b27"/>畫像，此為同也；州曰<placeName key="PL000000020250">歷下</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000009928"><anchor xml:id="beg0825sgsz12"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>始</sic><corr>姑</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0825sgsz12"/>蘇</placeName>，遇者曰<persName key="A012152">陸</persName>與<lb
ed="T" n="0825b28"/><persName key="A012147">馮</persName>，此為異焉。斯蓋見聞不齊，記錄因別也。<lb
ed="T" n="0825b29"/>原夫聖人之應身<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1665"/>也，或南或北，或<name>漢</name>或胡，或<pb ed="T" n="0825c" xml:id="T50.2061.0825c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0825c01"/>平常之形，或怪差之質，故令聞見必也有<lb
ed="T" n="0825c02"/>殊，復使傳揚，自然多說。譬猶千里之外，望<lb
ed="T" n="0825c03"/>日月以皆同，其時邊旁雲物狀貌有異耳。<lb
ed="T" n="0825c04"/>既是不思議應現矣，則隨緣赴感，肆是難<lb
ed="T" n="0825c05"/>同。可發例云：「所傳聞異辭也。」</p>
